{"word":"G2523 - καθίζω - kathízō - kath-id'-zo - Continue","slug":"G2523","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">καθίζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>kathízō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>kath-id'-zo"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Continue"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03BA;&#x03B1;&#x03B8;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03B6;&#x03C9; - kathizo&#x0304;</b> - <i>kath-id'-zo</i><p/>Another (active) form for <a href=\"#/G2516\">G2516</a>; to <i>seat down</i>, that is, <i>set</i> (figuratively <i>appoint</i>); intransitively to <i>sit</i> (down); figuratively to <i>settle</i> (<i>hover</i>, <i>dwell</i>): - continue, set, sit (down), tarry."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2516\">G2516</a>, <a href=\"#/G2521\">G2521</a>"}]}